  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      examination of the importance of the use of X-ray in bariatric surgery outcome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      the x-ray will be used in order to evaluate the number of complications occured during
      bariatric surgeries such as bleeding, leak, etc. a retrospective analysis of patients with
      those complications will be performed and the presence of the x-ray and its findings will
      also be documented.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
